acity for each of the pipes for the first nine months of this year?It would be very helpful if you or someone could respond this afternoon. Thanks!_________________________Gay MayeuxVice President, Investor RelationsEnron Corp.1400 Smith Street, EB 4931aHouston, Texas 77002Phone:  713-853-9905Cell:      713-416-8821Fax:      713-646-3002email:    gay.mayeux@enron.com</data>
