      <data key="e_body">Jim:Thanks for getting people together. There are (at least) 3 things going on here:1) Coordinate PG&amp;E/SCE2) Edison &quot;meet and confer&quot; (on Monday?  sez Williams) to discuss the prehearing conference at the PUC on Nov. 7th.3) Edison meeting to discuss settlement of PX credit that Fielder s coordinating.2 and 3 are, of course, extremely related.  It is critical that gov t affairs (you or me or both) be completely involved in items 2 and 3 above, and frankly, i think that one of us needs to be at the meeting.  No finger pointing, but our litigation strategy with edison thus far has been wanting.We have a number yet for the call?Best,Jeff</data>
