ngs.2:39 The food arrives. We are allasleep with ourheads on the table. The waiter wakes usup. We eatevery fucking bit of our food. Mostof the restaurantpatrons around us are disgusted. Wedon t give ashit.The tab is $112 with tip.2:46 I m sleepy.9:12 I wake up next to a strange woman.She is thebartender at Katz s. She is not pretty.</data>
