      <data key="e_body">X-FileName: kam keiser 7-11-02.PSTErrol,Here are the bankruptcy post-id s that need to be calculated tonight.  You probably don t have access to the Canadian book so you can get it from Jeremy or use my computer.  The right one has portcalc up, kkeiser &amp; tamu96ddd.They might need to be on inexact for basis and index.Once those are done, can you email the id # s to John Powell, Debbie Brackett and Stephanie McGinnis?ThanksKamcall me if you have any problems713-398-4735</data>
